Normal-school graduates posted to villages the highway ignores, each one a state employee, each one nineteen and underpaid and angry: there is no better soil in Mexico. The SNTE's men take names at the section meetings. Othón takes more.

@othon_montana
title: La Montaña
subtitle: Deep work in Guerrero — masses, not guns, whatever the young men in the hills are saying.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer == 0
